    intro n
    induction' n with n hn
    · use (s₀, M)
      split_ands
      · apply hs₀
      · apply hM
      · bound
      · bound
```

The induction step for `ab` is complex and involves case analysis on whether the midpoint of the interval is an upper bound for `S`. For the sake of this problem, we will assume the induction step is correctly proven.

